data.description: Highly upgraded home with 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and kitchen island. Master bathroom and upstairs guest bathroom both feature dual sinks. Backyard has a Pebbletec pool with built in table and water feature, mature trees and shrubs, and covered patio has misting system for those hot days.  Community features two parks. One park is gated and only available to community members. Private park includes half court basketball, swing set, grass play area, covered picnic tables and other playground equipment. Close to freeways, Desert Ridge Marketplace and restaurants.
